<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 03:01:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>警方调查凶手在悉尼购物中心袭击中针对女性的行为</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/police-probe-killers-targeting-of-women-in-sydney-mall-attack/articleshow/109297578.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109297578.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚警方周一表示，他们正在调查一名 40 岁患有精神疾病的男子持大刀在悉尼一家购物中心漫步时似乎以女性为目标，导致六人死亡、十几人受伤的原因。唯一遇难者是30岁的巴基斯坦男子法拉兹·塔希尔(Faraz Tahir)，他被刺伤时正在担任保安。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/police-probe-killers-targeting-of-women-in-sydney-mall-attack/articleshow/109297578.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯提出新的停火协议，要求在释放人质之前停止敌对行动六周</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-proposes-new-ceasefire-deal-demands-six-week-break-from-hostilities-before-release-of-hostages/articleshow/109297503.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109297503.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在加沙持续敌对行动期间，哈马斯拒绝了以色列的停火提议，之后向调解人提出了一项停火和释放人质协议，要求以色列遵守为期六周的停火协议，然后再接收该恐怖组织自 10 月以来扣押的 129 名人质中的任何一个。以色列时报7日援引希伯来日报《国土报》的报道报道。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:30:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-proposes-new-ceasefire-deal-demands-six-week-break-from-hostilities-before-release-of-hostages/articleshow/109297503.cms</guid></item><item><title>封口费审判前，特朗普追捕法官和地方检察官</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-goes-after-the-judge-and-prosecutors-in-his-hush-money-case-in-last-rally-before-trial-begins/articleshow/109297443.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109297443.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;前总统唐纳德·特朗普猛烈批评纽约检察官，将他即将到来的审判称为“共产主义表演审判”。特朗普在宾夕法尼亚州赢得了支持，解决了法律挑战，并发誓要在竞选对手乔·拜登总统的同时打击重罪指控。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:13:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-goes-after-the-judge-and-prosecutors-in-his-hush-money-case-in-last-rally-before-trial-begins/articleshow/109297443.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列：时机成熟时将准确定价；战时内阁召开会议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-will-exact-price-when-time-is-right-war-cabinet-holds-meeting/articleshow/109297332.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109297332.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列战时内阁正在讨论对伊朗的无人机和导弹袭击进行报复。报复的时间和规模存在分歧。甘茨计划在适当的时候建立区域联盟进行报复。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 23:49:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-will-exact-price-when-time-is-right-war-cabinet-holds-meeting/articleshow/109297332.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗用导弹和无人机对以色列发动前所未有的袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-hits-israel-with-missiles-drones-in-unprecedented-strike/articleshow/109297323.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109297323.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗从其领土对以色列发动大规模空袭，发射了 300 多架无人机和导弹，以回应对伊朗驻叙利亚大使馆大楼的袭击。这次袭击造成轻微损害，没有造成人员伤亡，导致该地区紧张局势升级。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 23:46:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-hits-israel-with-missiles-drones-in-unprecedented-strike/articleshow/109297323.cms</guid></item><item><title>因伊朗和以色列紧张局势而陷入混乱，航空公司争先恐后地寻找安全飞行路线</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/sent-into-a-tizzy-by-iran-israel-tensions-airlines-scramble-to-find-safe-flight-paths/articleshow/109294237.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109294237.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 19:49:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/sent-into-a-tizzy-by-iran-israel-tensions-airlines-scramble-to-find-safe-flight-paths/articleshow/109294237.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称与美国及其盟国“结盟”对抗伊朗</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-army-says-countered-iran-in-coalition-with-us-allies/articleshow/109294132.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109294132.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 19:25:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-army-says-countered-iran-in-coalition-with-us-allies/articleshow/109294132.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗警告不要回应袭击，以色列保持警惕：你需要知道的一切</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-on-alert-as-iran-warns-against-responding-to-attack-all-you-need-to-know/articleshow/109292752.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109292752.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗首次对以色列发动直接攻击，引起国际谴责。美国支持以色列，而英国则批评这次袭击。俄罗斯、中国敦促克制。哈马斯支持伊朗。印度为其在以色列的公民提供求助热线电话。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 16:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-on-alert-as-iran-warns-against-responding-to-attack-all-you-need-to-know/articleshow/109292752.cms</guid></item><item><title>刚果民主共和国山体滑坡已造成至少 12 人死亡，逾 50 人仍失踪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/dr-congo-landslide-kills-at-least-12-more-than-50-still-missing/articleshow/109292037.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109292037.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;刚果迪巴亚卢布韦(Dibaya Lubwe)因大雨发生山沟塌陷，造成12人死亡、50人失踪。开西河地区发生山体滑坡。生存机会渺茫。气候专家强调脆弱的城市规划。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 15:14:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/dr-congo-landslide-kills-at-least-12-more-than-50-still-missing/articleshow/109292037.cms</guid></item><item><title>是什么让印第安溪岛成为“亿万富翁地堡”？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/what-makes-indian-creek-island-a-billionaire-bunker/articleshow/109291287.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109291287.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;杰夫·贝索斯 (Jeff Bezos) 在迈阿密印第安河岛上购买了一座价值 9000 万美元的豪宅，被称为“亿万富翁地堡”，拥有度假式的生活、海景以及私人警察部队和乡村俱乐部等专属设施。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 14:11:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/what-makes-indian-creek-island-a-billionaire-bunker/articleshow/109291287.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗对以色列的袭击引起加沙巴勒斯坦人的钦佩</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-attack-on-israel-stirs-admiration-among-gaza-palestinians/articleshow/109291173.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109291173.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙对伊朗袭击以色列的反应不一。来自中华人民共和国和伊斯兰圣战组织的支持。以色列对加沙地带的空袭仍在继续，造成人员伤亡。巴勒斯坦人对伊朗的动机持谨慎态度。该地区局势依然高度紧张。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 13:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-attack-on-israel-stirs-admiration-among-gaza-palestinians/articleshow/109291173.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰之外：俄罗斯如何试图将其地缘政治影响力扩展到全球</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/beyond-ukraine-how-russia-is-trying-to-extend-its-geopolitical-reach-across-the-globe/articleshow/109290939.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109290939.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国 RUSI 最近的一份报告显示，俄罗斯的全球影响力随着其非常规战争策略的实施而增强。该报告强调了俄罗斯在欧洲的秘密行动、在非洲部署雇佣军以及与中亚和欧洲穆斯林社区的接触。地缘政治影响力的扩大引发了乌克兰持续冲突的担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 13:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/beyond-ukraine-how-russia-is-trying-to-extend-its-geopolitical-reach-across-the-globe/articleshow/109290939.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国是否在菲律宾招募“潜伏小组”军人？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/is-china-recruiting-sleeper-cell-military-members-in-the-philippines/articleshow/109290936.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109290936.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;布劳纳将军透露，中国曾因在西菲律宾海从事间谍活动而接触过菲律宾军官。追踪到一个网站的中国招聘引发了担忧。参议员询问中国签证，而分析人士则讨论南海紧张局势加剧的情况下的安全风险和全球间谍活动。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 13:45:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/is-china-recruiting-sleeper-cell-military-members-in-the-philippines/articleshow/109290936.cms</guid></item><item><title>里希·苏纳克表示，英国击落了“多架”伊朗攻击无人机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-shot-down-a-number-of-iranian-attack-drones-says-rishi-sunak/articleshow/109289312.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109289312.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相苏纳克证实英国战机拦截了针对以色列的伊朗无人机，并敦促各方保持克制。他赞扬飞行员的勇敢，谴责伊朗的升级，并重申对以色列安全的支持。英国皇家空军支持“着色行动”以反击伊朗的袭击。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 12:30:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-shot-down-a-number-of-iranian-attack-drones-says-rishi-sunak/articleshow/109289312.cms</guid></item><item><title>由于紧张局势加剧，伊朗机场关闭至周一早上</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-airports-shut-until-monday-morning-amid-rising-tensions/articleshow/109287510.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109287510.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据伊朗机场和空中航行公司称，由于关闭，德黑兰梅赫拉巴德机场以及设拉子、伊斯法罕、布什尔、克尔曼、伊拉姆和萨南达季等全国各地机场的国内航班也被取消，直到周一早上。伊朗西部领空的航班。目前的局势也影响了整个中东地区的主要航空公司。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 10:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-airports-shut-until-monday-morning-amid-rising-tensions/articleshow/109287510.cms</guid></item><item><title>“忘记”哈马斯袭击：以色列和爱尔兰就爱尔兰总理首次谴责加沙战争的讲话发生争执</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/forgot-hamas-attack-israel-ireland-spar-over-irish-pms-first-speech-condemning-war-in-gaza/articleshow/109287281.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109287281.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;爱尔兰新任总理西蒙·哈里斯 (Simon Harris) 在他的第一次公开演讲中没有提及 10 月 7 日的哈马斯大屠杀，但在演讲中确实提到了加沙战争，以色列外交部对他进行了措辞严厉的谴责。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 09:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/forgot-hamas-attack-israel-ireland-spar-over-irish-pms-first-speech-condemning-war-in-gaza/articleshow/109287281.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普试图推翻选举失败的后果将提交给最高法院</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fallout-from-trumps-bid-to-overturn-election-loss-heads-to-supreme-court/articleshow/109287527.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109287527.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国最高法院就特朗普试图避免起诉和袭击国会大厦的指控提起诉讼。费舍尔面临阻碍。特朗普封口费审判开始。法院推翻了科罗拉多州的裁决。特朗普声称拥有总统豁免权。法律专家预计审判结果将在 11 月 5 日之前公布。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 10:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fallout-from-trumps-bid-to-overturn-election-loss-heads-to-supreme-court/articleshow/109287527.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击以色列后俄罗斯敦促“克制”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/russia-urges-restraint-after-iranian-attack-on-israel/articleshow/109287334.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109287334.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在伊朗对以色列进行导弹和无人机袭击后，俄罗斯呼吁保持克制。莫斯科对事态升级表示担忧，并指出中东局势可能会加剧不稳定。俄罗斯外长拉夫罗夫与伊朗阿米尔阿卜杜拉希安进行了交谈。俄罗斯外交部表示，拉夫罗夫重申“坚决谴责”以色列本月在叙利亚发动的袭击，造成伊朗将军死亡。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 09:56:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/russia-urges-restraint-after-iranian-attack-on-israel/articleshow/109287334.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃及否认关闭领空并确认继续空中航行</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/egypt-denies-closure-of-its-airspace-and-confirms-continuation-of-air-navigation/articleshow/109287187.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109287187.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃及政府驳斥了埃及领空被关闭的说法。埃及内阁媒体中心今天表示，除飞往空域关闭国家的航班外，埃及所有机场均正常运行，航班继续按计划飞行。尽管社交媒体和某些媒体上流传着谣言，但该中心保证空中航行不会中断。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 09:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/egypt-denies-closure-of-its-airspace-and-confirms-continuation-of-air-navigation/articleshow/109287187.cms</guid></item><item><title>悉尼袭击中丧生的巴基斯坦男子：社区团体</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pakistani-man-among-those-killed-in-sydney-attack-community-groups/articleshow/109285960.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109285960.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据两个当地社区团体称，一名 30 岁的巴基斯坦男子周日在悉尼一家购物中心周末持刀袭击中丧生，这名保安是一名保安。澳大利亚巴基斯坦全国协会和艾哈迈迪亚穆斯林社区表示，法拉兹·塔希尔被一名持刀男子杀害，该男子还杀害了五名妇女。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 08:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pakistani-man-among-those-killed-in-sydney-attack-community-groups/articleshow/109285960.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>